ent-AU14UPPclothingapparelvendor = UPP apparel vendor
    .desc =
        An automated dispenser rack, hooked up to a small storage of Union of Progressive Peoples apparel. Standard issue aboard naval vessels, military outposts, corporate-science installations and civilian colonies across the frontier. Manufactured to outfit personnel rapidly following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization.
        For full operational readiness, select one item from each section: fatigues with a webbing, footwear, gloves, headgear, armor, backpack, belt and a pouch.
ent-AU14UPPequipmentvendor = UPP equipment vendor
    .desc =
        An automated dispenser rack, hooked up to a small storage of Union of Progressive Peoples equipment. Stocked with medical supplies and field gear for rapid deployment following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization. The interface is intentionally simple, even someone with tunnel-vision and frostbite can operate it.
        Rapid-issue protocol: prioritize medical supplies, a ration pack, an e-tool and sandbags.
ent-AU14UPPMedicalVendor = UPP medical vendor
    .desc =
        An automated medical rack, hooked up to a compact stock of Union of Progressive Peoples trauma supplies. Standard issue for corpsmen aboard naval vessels, outposts and colonies where casualties arrive faster than reinforcements. Designed for rapid reconstitution of combat medics following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency call-up.
        Corpsman protocol: select the essential equipment set, storage and limited medications.
ent-AU14UPPaircrewvendor = UPP aircrew vendor
    .desc =
        An automated dispenser rack, hooked up to a small storage of Union of Progressive Peoples aircrew flight and support gear. Engineered to get flight personnel flight-ready in seconds after cryogenic hypersleep or scramble orders.
        Aircrew protocol: select a set of fatigues, the essential medical equipment and storage kit.
ent-AU14UPPcommandvendor = UPP command vendor
    .desc = An automated command rack, hooked up to a restricted storage of Union of Progressive Peoples command-leadership equipment. Manufactured to equip commanding personnel following cryogenic hypersleep or an emergency directive is issued.
ent-AU14UPPgunnerequipment = UPP automatic rifleman equipment vendor
    .desc = An automated weapons rack, hooked up to a small armory of Union of Progressive Peoples light-machine gun equipment. Standard issue for designated LMG crews on naval vessels and outposts. Built to bring fire support online rapidly after cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization.
ent-AU14UPPSectionLeaderVendor = UPP section leader vendor
    .desc = An automated equipment rack, hooked up to a compact storage of Union of Progressive Peoples section-leadership equipment. Designed for immediate readiness following cryogenic hypersleep or rapid mobilization orders.
ent-AU14UPPWeaponsVendor = UPP weapons rack
    .desc =
        An automated weapons rack, hooked up to a small armory of Union of Progressive Peoples weaponry. Standard issue across the frontier where threats can appear without warning. Engineered to arm personnel in seconds following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization.
        For immediate combat readiness: select a primary weapon kit and a sidearm.
ent-AU14UPPSpecialWeaponsVendor = UPP special weapons rack
    .desc =
        An automated special weapons rack, hooked up to a restricted armory of Union of Progressive Peoples heavy and breaching ordnance. Standard issue only for qualified operators. Engineered to deliver overwhelming firepower the instant cryogenic hypersleep ends or an emergency mobilization is called.
        Special weapons protocol: one weapon system of choice with a full ammunition loadout and explosives.
ent-AU14UPPAirCrewWeaponsVendor = UPP aircrew weapons rack
    .desc = An automated rack hooked up to a small storage of aircrew weapons.
ent-AU14ComtechGearVendorUPP = UPP combat technicians gear rack
    .desc = An automated gear rack for combat technicians.
ent-AU14MilitaryPolicemanVendorUPP = UPP commissariat police equipment rack
    .desc = An automated rack hooked up to a small storage of military police equipment.
ent-AU14UPPRequisitionVendor = UPP automated requisitions vendor
    .desc = An automated supply rack hooked up to a big storage of various firearms, ammunitions, explosives, load carrying equipment and other miscellaneous items.
